  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <div class="content">
      <div class="intro">
        <h1>
          Our services
        </h1>
        <p>
          Comprising strictly of 7 people, we are uniquely aware of each of our strengths and capabilities. All members work on all projects in a flat hierarchy, allowing for high impact creativity and high quality output. We bring all of our personal curiosity to complement our professional expertise.
        </p>
        <p>
          We currently offer various professional and technical services related to user experience research and design.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h1>
          Professional services
        </h1>
        <p>
          <ul>
            <li>Research and study design</li>
            <li>Consultation and Strategy</li>
            <li>Education and Training</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h1>
          Technical services
        </h1>
        <p>
          <ul>
            <li>User Research</li>
            <li>User Experience Design</li>
            <li>Prototype Testing</li>
            <li>Design Workshops</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
      </div>

      <CTA />
    </div>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .fixed-header {
    @apply fixed bottom-auto top-0;
    @apply border-default bg-default text-default;
  }
  .modal.is-open {
    @apply block;
  }

  .content {
    display: flex;
    max-width: 1200px;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: #00000010;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    align-self: stretch;
  }

  .intro {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 1rem 0rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  li {
    list-style-type: disc;
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>